IPL matches are back on the screen // Prime Minister is campaigning in Bihar // Operation Sindoor has become a political slogan // Satellite imagery has established how hard we hit the Pakistani bases.
Yet we are hemming & hawing over this one question of lost jets? What is this obsession over a conflict with zero losses? 
If a clear answer was not to be given - why agree for the interview?? You thought that an international outlet like Bloomberg will NOT ask uncomfortable questions?  Everyone is not Godi.

Discussing this on Sunday Night Livestream along with tons of other questions that u might have on the episodes we have done! (Including Norway (mis)adventure! ;)
